{"tid":412621,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲鍾意西式紅茶??","createTime":"2017-09-24T22:03:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T04:13:27.000Z","uid":13752,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c5ea3a5ed6bf1cc6c0c0dc4eab3128b55e7bb26","tid":412621,"uid":13752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T22:03:55.000Z","msg":"我岩岩係twinings 度訂咗一堆茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多唔同味嘅茶係UK先有 香港店無 加上香港賣得貴好多<br />\n同埋有好多茶UK版茶味都會濃好多 例如伯爵茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我買咗堆水果紅茶/水果綠茶/薄荷茶/紅茶<br />\n茶包嘅價錢 圍返都係$0.9 一包茶包<br />\n500g嘅罐裝伯爵紅茶茶葉 都係$130<br />\n6克左右茶葉一杯茶 圍返都係$1.5<br />\n我買咗好多 total275個茶包 先$150運費<br />\n我用到呢$150好盡 岩岩好 再加多樣野就加$77運費<br />\n計埋運費 一杯茶都唔洗$2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又平又高質過香港其他牌子好多...<br />\nTwinings仲有好多其他茶 大吉嶺 印度茶etc.<br />\n呢個係英國好出名嘅品牌 好多人去英國都會買黎做手信<br />\n但其實上網訂都唔貴 真係鍾意茶可以去睇下<br />\n佢依加新開ac仲有20%OFF<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我等緊到貨 應該呢幾日到 到時再開箱影相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw下次想試另一隻牌子 Fortnum &amp; Mason<br />\n聽講正過twinings 係英女皇御用品牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bae20f6ba8f19f03651c7d8c81a001a816ccd33","tid":412621,"uid":35746,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T22:25:04.000Z","msg":"中式茶正d"},{"pid":"a522e05eca917c314106334e2dc3b3467b00e86c","tid":412621,"uid":90702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T22:56:03.000Z","msg":"好想試水果茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等我又睇下先"},{"pid":"ccb5bf0640d47c0fa3de3d02d0b985bcdc0bd19d","tid":412621,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T22:57:37.000Z","msg":"點樣為之靚紅茶"},{"pid":"6191d36e7fd6313d37c1004d32a7dcb05f3f138a","tid":412621,"uid":49620,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T23:06:36.000Z","msg":"twinings都有打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ac15d8421c6e90f3d53190370c51a41fe44878","tid":412621,"uid":13752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T02:56:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中式茶正d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各有特式啦 綠茶我都鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e618bbadf2f25babda60af0984d0fa270772b3d5","tid":412621,"uid":13752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T02:57:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想試水果茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等我又睇下先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽講好香 但唔會有甜味 唔甜都好 健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbafce5c9f1faa3c7021fd3fa1fe9a05daece86d","tid":412621,"uid":13752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T02:58:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點樣為之靚紅茶</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前上網google過 其實隻隻牌子都有人話好話唔好<br />\n我覺得 自己鍾意飲先係最重要<br />\n唔啱你口味幾靚嘅茶都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"453b6721257b4bbe9da32a82c167195a8fad2f90","tid":412621,"uid":27504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T02:59:35.000Z","msg":"Fortnum嘅queen anne<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a50020d3bc30d43828448e6b393f4554be34bca","tid":412621,"uid":13752,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:02:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>twinings都有打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講得出呢句肯定你戇撚鳩<br />\nUK總公司請我係香港討論區做打手？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係就好喇 我唔撚洗比錢買茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔係係香港店買 都唔係推緊香港店<br />\n討論叫打手？post都講咗F&amp;M我想試<br />\n但比twinings貴 我想試咗平嘅先<br />\n咁請問你又推薦邊隻牌子啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d847a843e5312b0681172fd9ee3a8db2f81005b8","tid":412621,"uid":13752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:03:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Fortnum嘅queen anne<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n諗住試咗平嘅牌子先買貴 係咪真係咁好飲？<br />\n上網見啲人勁推佢啲水果茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e45f2c0b9c62d702c1658121c871b8e9d9c29f","tid":412621,"uid":27504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:11:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Fortnum嘅queen anne<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n諗住試咗平嘅牌子先買貴 係咪真係咁好飲？<br />\n上網見啲人勁推佢啲水果茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加奶好香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 茶包嚟講好抵屌，濃過twinings好多，twinings我起碼用兩個茶包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我麻麻哋水果茶，之前買過fortnum隻蘋果茶聞落好香但味比較淡"},{"pid":"808c2010d193ce3473bcf1f3e16c78924f655e2d","tid":412621,"uid":13752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:21:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Fortnum嘅queen anne<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n諗住試咗平嘅牌子先買貴 係咪真係咁好飲？<br />\n上網見啲人勁推佢啲水果茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加奶好香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 茶包嚟講好抵屌，濃過twinings好多，twinings我起碼用兩個茶包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我麻麻哋水果茶，之前買過fortnum隻蘋果茶聞落好香但味比較淡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上網睇都話果茶得陣味香 可能到時要加少少蜜糖會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過一定要試咗原味係點先落糖 好鍾意啲茶香味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我一下訂咗15隻茶 等緊佢送黎 好興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見twinings嘅伯爵茶係UK以外地區買到嘅係黃色茶包(淡味)<br />\nUK版本嘅係黑色嘅就係濃味版 呢隻我買咗茶葉<br />\n希望會濃味啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044439a1ac0087d1ab601a091ea6f5552e47df33","tid":412621,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T08:10:39.000Z","msg":"Twinings香港好貴，見到桃茶同d水果茶想買 ，60蚊盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n等你repo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我有d強逼症，好唔鐘意次次沖到唔同濃度澀度，好想次次一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以最近轉左冷泡......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f94423529dd21017c5a61a8c6005ad74b7315de","tid":412621,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T08:11:45.000Z","msg":"同埋最近買左d 20蚊一盒水果茶包， 一落水就極快出顏色，又甜又怪味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4f0d8a7380968eedeaa58b77c377b362dfbfa1","tid":412621,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T08:14:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋最近買左d 20蚊一盒水果茶包， 一落水就極快出顏色，又甜又怪味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n759個d 三角茶包?"},{"pid":"63ade184249940f1ab096ef6fd4fdce9127c3922","tid":412621,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T08:22:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同埋最近買左d 20蚊一盒水果茶包， 一落水就極快出顏色，又甜又怪味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n759個d 三角茶包?</blockquote><br />\n係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  都唔鬼知邊度出既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見佢咁多包又咁平，其實我都應該知伏....."},{"pid":"ab85694221e565b375611ae9c06de5e575a65f98","tid":412621,"uid":13752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T17:32:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Twinings香港好貴，見到桃茶同d水果茶想買 ，60蚊盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n等你repo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我有d強逼症，好唔鐘意次次沖到唔同濃度澀度，好想次次一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以最近轉左冷泡......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好啊 等我到貨 我都好心急啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n桃茶我其實都想買港版 我唔見UK有純蜜桃茶賣<br />\n得蜜桃+車厘子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n一般UK版水果茶係1.69英磅1盒 有20個茶包<br />\n乘返港幣係$18左右一盒 所以香港真係貴到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n熱泡計準時間同埋落嘅水應該都唔會次次唔同味<br />\n我都唔鍾意唔同味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f95dc1dfbc625a4cc8464e16d37ca0083c6a709","tid":412621,"uid":13752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T17:34:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋最近買左d 20蚊一盒水果茶包， 一落水就極快出顏色，又甜又怪味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n怪味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 買隻咩味水果咁伏<br />\n香港真係咩都貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對比返外國 平嘅已經屌打埋香港賣得貴嘅茶"},{"pid":"7f1c228dea9050fb87570dfb5035c5e4fc57b7ea","tid":412621,"uid":43957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T17:39:22.000Z","msg":"Fortnum嘅famous tea勁正<br />\n包裝條嘢喺橙色嘅<br />\n有紅茶香味又要少少花香味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經買咗好多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca380e5a8b37945f0ec98ab70cc92ed3ac1d610","tid":412621,"uid":146467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T17:45:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我岩岩係twinings 度訂咗一堆茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多唔同味嘅茶係UK先有 香港店無 加上香港賣得貴好多<br />\n同埋有好多茶UK版茶味都會濃好多 例如伯爵茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我買咗堆水果紅茶/水果綠茶/薄荷茶/紅茶<br />\n茶包嘅價錢 圍返都係$0.9 一包茶包<br />\n500g嘅罐裝伯爵紅茶茶葉 都係$130<br />\n6克左右茶葉一杯茶 圍返都係$1.5<br />\n我買咗好多 total275個茶包 先$150運費<br />\n我用到呢$150好盡 岩岩好 再加多樣野就加$77運費<br />\n計埋運費 一杯茶都唔洗$2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又平又高質過香港其他牌子好多...<br />\nTwinings仲有好多其他茶 大吉嶺 印度茶etc.<br />\n呢個係英國好出名嘅品牌 好多人去英國都會買黎做手信<br />\n但其實上網訂都唔貴 真係鍾意茶可以去睇下<br />\n佢依加新開ac仲有20%OFF<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我等緊到貨 應該呢幾日到 到時再開箱影相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw下次想試另一隻牌子 Fortnum &amp; Mason<br />\n聽講正過twinings 係英女皇御用品牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都鍾意紅茶～"},{"pid":"f036979fc90a54d1a3cd60c1a6edc1885d4c0d92","tid":412621,"uid":13752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T18:53:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Fortnum嘅famous tea勁正<br />\n包裝條嘢喺橙色嘅<br />\n有紅茶香味又要少少花香味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經買咗好多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係香港買定係都係上佢個網訂<br />\n我諗住遲啲都會買一堆 但要研究下佢送唔送香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410417b04b9bd36e8e92a7265e5a707f572453b0","tid":412621,"uid":70518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T22:16:10.000Z","msg":"斯里蘭卡-dilmah<br />\n全人手採集 同用嫩葉<br />\n所以飲落個單寧唔會好粗...焗耐左都唔怕"},{"pid":"33204fa3a260a052fb39a0a8f3202e37386c148d","tid":412621,"uid":78304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T22:22:22.000Z","msg":"F&amp;M 伯爵茶最好飲, queen anne個人就唔中意, 感覺都唔知飲緊乜咁"},{"pid":"4834ff07b0aa9ecd9dfe7a2aa686eaa97299a0f0","tid":412621,"uid":78304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T22:32:43.000Z","msg":"大吉嶺 同Assam 我都係會揀F&amp;M,咁既價錢有FTGFOP 同 TGFOP邊度揾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ntwinings 既 prince of wales 幾好,但唔知點解上次買果包茶包好飲過而家手頭上既茶葉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbreakfast tea我買開茶包,方便就算. 紅茶都係中意臺灣國產既蜜香紅茶多D"}]}